---
---

<section class="w-full bg-[#F3EFE9] py-[100px] md:py-[130px] px-6 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
    
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="inline-block bg-white/90 text-[#3c3a37] text-[12px] font-medium tracking-wider uppercase rounded-full px-5 py-[8px] shadow-[0_2px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)]">
            What I Believe
        </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Title -->
    <h2 class="font-sans font-medium text-[38px] md:text-[68px] leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#282725] mb-5">
        The stuff that<br />
        actually <span class="text-[#995531]">matters.</span>
    </h2>

    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <p class="text-[#68625d] text-[16px] md:text-[16.5px] font-light max-w-[420px] mx-auto leading-[1.6] mb-[70px]">
        I've learned these the hard way over eight years of doing this work, and they guide every session I run.
    </p>

    <!-- Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 md:gap-6 text-left w-full max-w-[1080px] mx-auto">
        
        <!-- Card 01 -->
        <div class="bg-[#FCFBFA] rounded-[20px] px-8 py-8 md:px-[42px] md:py-[36px] w-full flex flex-col hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow duration-300">
            <span class="block font-serif italic text-[44px] text-[#995531] mb-3 leading-none tracking-[-0.02em] opacity-90">01</span>
            <h3 class="text-[#282725] text-[19px] md:text-[20px] font-medium mb-2 tracking-tight">The truth, but gently</h3>
            <p class="text-[#68625d] text-[14.5px] font-light leading-[1.6] max-w-[100%]">
                I'll always be straight with you. Not harsh, but real. That's how things actually change.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 02 -->
        <div class="bg-[#FCFBFA] rounded-[20px] px-8 py-8 md:px-[42px] md:py-[36px] w-full flex flex-col hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow duration-300">
            <span class="block font-serif italic text-[44px] text-[#995531] mb-3 leading-none tracking-[-0.02em] opacity-90">02</span>
            <h3 class="text-[#282725] text-[19px] md:text-[20px] font-medium mb-2 tracking-tight">Small shifts beat big overhauls</h3>
            <p class="text-[#68625d] text-[14.5px] font-light leading-[1.6] max-w-[100%]">
                Nobody sustains a complete life makeover overnight. We start small and build from there.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 03 -->
        <div class="bg-[#FCFBFA] rounded-[20px] px-8 py-8 md:px-[42px] md:py-[36px] w-full flex flex-col hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow duration-300">
            <span class="block font-serif italic text-[44px] text-[#995531] mb-3 leading-none tracking-[-0.02em] opacity-90">03</span>
            <h3 class="text-[#282725] text-[19px] md:text-[20px] font-medium mb-2 tracking-tight">Your life, your pace</h3>
            <p class="text-[#68625d] text-[14.5px] font-light leading-[1.6] max-w-[100%]">
                I'm not here to hand you a generic plan. Everything we do is built around how you actually live.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 04 -->
        <div class="bg-[#FCFBFA] rounded-[20px] px-8 py-8 md:px-[42px] md:py-[36px] w-full flex flex-col hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow duration-300">
            <span class="block font-serif italic text-[44px] text-[#995531] mb-3 leading-none tracking-[-0.02em] opacity-90">04</span>
            <h3 class="text-[#282725] text-[19px] md:text-[20px] font-medium mb-2 tracking-tight">Rest isn't lazy</h3>
            <p class="text-[#68625d] text-[14.5px] font-light leading-[1.6] max-w-[100%]">
                You've probably been told to push through. I'm telling you to stop. That's where the real work begins.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>
